Just in case you\xe2\x80\x99ve been living on a desert island for the last two years, allow us to catch you up: Voice interfaces are the latest tech trend and they\xe2\x80\x99re showing up everywhere, from smartphones to smart speakers. As of Tuesday, even your favorite DVR is getting in on the voice action: 
\xc2\xa0is adding two new products to its 
, with the Bolt Vox, and Mini Vox, confirming earlier rumors.
Both devices come with TiVo\xe2\x80\x99s new\xc2\xa0Vox remote, with a nearly identical layout to previous Bolt remotes except for two notable additions, including a prominent light-blue microphone button, and \xe2\x80\x94 for the first time on a TiVo remote \xe2\x80\x94 a dedicated Netflix button.
he TiVo Bolt Vox, with up to 4K Ultra HD resolution, which includes four integrated tuners starts at $200 for the 500 GB model. You can also choose a larger 1TB model for $299, or go for the gusto with the top of the line 3TB model at $499.
he TiVo Mini Vox, which is a companion to the Bolt Vox, letting you access content at up to 4K Ultra HD resolution on other TVs in your home, is $180.
You can also buy the Vox remote (available in black or white) on its own for $40. It can be used with existing Bolt boxes as-is, or with TiVo Mini and 
set-top boxes \xe2\x80\x94 but these require an additional Bluetooth module, bumping the price to $45.
iVo has clearly done its homework on the Vox voice commands: The company incorporates the best features of 
\xe2\x80\x9cShow me movies with Tom Cruise,\xe2\x80\x9d then refine the query by saying things like, \xe2\x80\x9cOnly the comedies\xe2\x80\x9d or \xe2\x80\x9cThe one where he says, \xe2\x80\x98Show me the money.\xe2\x80\x99\xe2\x80\x9d
he voice commands also work with playback control, with commands like \xe2\x80\x9cSkip it,\xe2\x80\x9d which will automatically jump you past the ads on a recorded program. Speaking of skipping, you\xe2\x80\x99ll find three new buttons on the Vox remote: A skip button (previously you had to use the \xe2\x80\x9cD\xe2\x80\x9d button to skip ads), a Netflix quick key \xe2\x80\x94 another Roku-inspired move \xe2\x80\x94 and of course the microphone button, which you need to press to initiate a voice command.
Bolt Vox and Mini Vox users will also benefit from TiVo\xe2\x80\x99s latest user experience update, which makes it easier to see what\xe2\x80\x99s streaming on each TiVo box in your home, while also improving some of the personalization features.
