Our take on the TiVo Vox\xe2\x84\xa2 Remote\r\n                        \r\n                        
Find your favorites faster with the Vox Remote
Use just your voice to search for shows to watch or record, change channels, launch an app, or skip commercials on your recordings. When you say the word, TiVo simultaneously searches across your live TV, recordings and streaming services to deliver personalized results based on what you watch and when you watch it.
he Vox Remote can also control power, input, volume and mute on your TV and/or home theater receiver.
brings the power of voice control to the TiVo experience
just press the blue "Voice" button, say your command, and let TiVo do the rest
skip commercials on recordings by pressing the "Voice" button and saying "Skip it"
IR/RF signal eliminates line-of-sight requirements \xe2\x80\x94 ideal for in-cabinet setups
warranty: 1 year parts, 90 days labor
