alk to TiVo with New VOX Remote and BOLT DV
iVo today announced a new suite of products that bring voice capabilities to new and existing DVRs. There is a new $40 
\xc2\xa0that\xe2\x80\x99s priced from $200 to $500. Lastly,\xc2\xa0
iVo VOX Remote allows you to use your voice to search across live TV, DVR recordings, video-on-demand and various online streaming services like Netflix, Hulu, VUDU, Amazon Prime Video and more. Searches also deliver personalized entertainment recommendations based on viewing habits. And, unlike many other TV platforms, TiVo lets users 
refine their voice searches in a natural way
. For example, simply say \xe2\x80\x9cShow me movies with Tom Cruise,\xe2\x80\x9d then refine the query by saying, \xe2\x80\x9cOnly the comedies\xe2\x80\x9d or \xe2\x80\x9cThe one where he says, \xe2\x80\x98Show me the money.\xe2\x80\x99\xe2\x80\x9d
Introducing the all-new TiVo BOLT VOX, Mini VOX, and VOX Remote, available October 29. Ready to 
In addition to voice, the TiVo BOLT VOX and TiVo Mini VOX feature the latest TiVo on-screen user experience. Combining visually rich design elements with enhanced usability, TiVo\xe2\x80\x99s next-generation user experience delivers spot-on personalized program predictions influenced by actual viewing habits. Poster art, actor and director biographies, sports team logos and more help viewers quickly cut through the clutter to find the shows they want and skip the ones they don\xe2\x80\x99t.
, a personalized prediction of shows to watch at that time influenced by prior viewing behavior \xe2\x80\x93 all without leaving the TV viewing experience.
